      <title>经济学家呼吁中国采取更多行动对抗通货紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/china-leaves-economists-wanting-more-action-to-defeat-deflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国进一步加大对经济的支持力度，承诺为低迷的房地产行业和负债累累的地方政府提供更多援助。但官员们仍未让经济学家相信他们已经采取了足够多的措施来战胜通货紧缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/china-leaves-economists-wanting-more-action-to-defeat-deflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 13:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
